    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Discretization error factor exceeds required level (achieved Gradation 3 vs. required Gradation 2), providing additional confidence margin. Six factors appropriately not assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table requirements. Validation results demonstrate CFD hemolysis predictions within experimental uncertainty across all five operating points (mean error 8.3%). RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all worst-case operating conditions. The 13-factor credibility assessment is complete and supports regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device. Credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended use decision.",
